quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  40,78,"GooŇč…óii Min imminii Nulaa…ďe ado maa. Hino e ma…ď…ďe, …ďe Min cifani maa fii mum; hino ma…ď…ďe, …ďe Min cifanaaki ma fii mum. Haananaa Nulaa…óo, addugol aaya, si wonaa e duŇčayee Allah. Si yamiroore Allah nden arii, goonga √Īaawirte meerente'en sooya nden √Īalnde."
  40,79,"Ko Allah woni wa…óiran…óo On neemoraa…ói …óin ko mba…ó…óoron, √Īaamon kadi e majji."
  40,80,"nafooje kadi hino ngoodani on e majji, e no njottoron e majji, haaju hittu…óo e berde mon. Ko e hoore majji e hoore laa…óe …óeen, woni ko ndonndete…óon."
  40,81,"Himo holla on maandeeji makko …óin. Ko hol…óum e Ma'andeeji Allah …óin, woni ko njeddoton?"
  40,82,"E …ďee yiilaaki ka leydi, …ďe ndaara ko holno battane …ďeya ado ma…ď…ďe mbattinirnoo? ∆Āen no …ďurunoo …ďe …óuude e sa…ótude doole e batteeji [wa…óaa…ói] ka leydi. Kono kon ko …ďe paggotonoo, duncanaano …ďe."
  40,83,"Nde Nulaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen addannoo…ďe …ďanngannduyeeji …óin, …ďe wewliri ganndal ko woni ka ma…ď…ďe kon. ∆Āe kuu…ďitiraa kon ko …ďe njalkitaynoo."
  40,84,"Nde …ďe nii'unoo lepte Amen …óen, …ďe mbi'i: "Min ngooŇč…óinii Allah tan, min yeddii kon ko men wonunoo e cirkannde"."
  40,85,"Kono ngooŇč…óinal ma…ď…ďe wonaano ko nafata …ďe, feewndo …ďe nji'unoo lepte Amen …óeen; …óum ko laawol Allah non, gooŇč…óii …óun yawtiino e jiyaa…ďe makko …ďeen. Yeddu…ďe …ďen sooyi …óon nden √Īalnde."